{
  "stem": "5103.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, a few-- my mother and father had hardly settled in, maybe six months, when they decided that there were so many Jewish children that had lost their parents, and their parents had gone, so they said, would you like a brother?",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, yes, I would like a brother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'd like a brother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'd like very much so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother had always told-- told me that she had a brother, and he died during the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I said, yes, I'd like it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we-- they went to the Red Cross to have a look if they could find somebody, the-- a child, that was sort of accessible to us, to see if they could give a child a home and adopt it.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when they went there, they were looking through the lists, and they discovered a name which came very familiar to them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it said, Herman Lezer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they thought, my god, this is something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My mother-- father's sister had a son, which was my first cousin, and her husband.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were sent to concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He escaped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They-- he was sent into hiding.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this is the little boy, [INAUDIBLE], who was my first cousin, whom was still alive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they decided to go and find-- find him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when they did, they found him on a farm in Friesland, in Holland, with farmers, who had very, very decent Christian family.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Very, very nice family.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they said that they were the only survivors there, like my father and mother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That was their aunt-- his uncle and aunt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they told me about it, that they were going to see him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then, they brought him home.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
